snippet.title: Little Cells - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
"Little Cells" is a quick & simple puzzle action game, released on Windows, MacOs & Linux.
Steam page: http://store.steampowered.com/app/352210
Android App: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fullybugged.littlecells
Other shops: http://littlecells.fullybugged.com:
